helpText1 = "Once upon a time there was a program, an app, that was made without care. As time went on, the programming mistakes multipied and grew into multi-cellular organisms. We call those organisms NSZombies and they threaten the very existence of the program.";
helpText2 = "But alas, all was not lost. You had the power to stop this onslaught. All that was required was unceasing vigil and repetitive dragging of the finger. As you remained true to your duty, the zombies could be held off.";